1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:01,100
The other day,

2
00:00:01,300 --> 00:00:02,240
President Kurogane's son and his wife

3
00:00:02,240 --> 00:00:04,640
were tragically killed
in a car accident.

4
00:00:04,700 --> 00:00:07,140
Though your circumstances
are a bit unusual,

5
00:00:07,540 --> 00:00:10,540
you are the president's
only blood relative.

6
00:00:10,580 --> 00:00:12,810
You must understand
your position.

7
00:00:12,850 --> 00:00:15,580
Don't you dare
take that tone with me.

8
00:00:15,580 --> 00:00:16,580
My apologies.

9
00:00:16,680 --> 00:00:19,320
Now that my position is clear,
I'm afraid I cannot.

10
00:00:19,320 --> 00:00:22,320
So... you're not my friend?

11
00:00:22,520 --> 00:00:24,490
That is correct.
My apologies.

12
00:00:24,490 --> 00:00:26,690
We've known each other
since grade school!

13
00:00:26,790 --> 00:00:28,600
To investigate and protect
the young lady's personal safety,

14
00:00:28,660 --> 00:00:31,770
and to report my findings,
is my job.

15
00:00:32,130 --> 00:00:32,930
So this whole time,

16
00:00:33,030 --> 00:00:34,930
you've been investigating
your own friend?

17
00:00:34,970 --> 00:00:37,570
As I have already stated,
we are not friends.

18
00:00:38,200 --> 00:00:40,940
For the sake of your happiness,

19
00:00:40,940 --> 00:00:41,940
President Kurogane will stop at nothing.

20
00:00:42,110 --> 00:00:43,540
If you don't want anything
to happen to Reika-san,

21
00:00:43,940 --> 00:00:45,250
then you will stay away from her.

22
00:00:45,250 --> 00:00:46,880
That is my sincere advice.

23
00:00:47,050 --> 00:00:47,650
Also,

24
00:00:47,650 --> 00:00:49,120
as for her little posse,

25
00:00:49,120 --> 00:00:50,380
and what they did to you,

26
00:00:50,580 --> 00:00:52,320
I've already reported it to the president.

27
00:00:54,820 --> 00:00:57,520
I heard Konno-san
is dropping out of school.

28
00:00:57,520 --> 00:00:58,520
What? Why?

29
00:00:59,260 --> 00:01:01,590
Her dad apparently got caught
for insider trading.

30
00:01:01,590 --> 00:01:02,060
That's crazy.

31
00:01:02,060 --> 00:01:04,500
And I heard Kaitani-san
is, like, an escort.

32
00:01:04,500 --> 00:01:05,530
Seriously? No way.

33
00:01:05,570 --> 00:01:07,030
I know, right?

34
00:01:07,030 --> 00:01:08,770
And get this, Mikami-san...

35
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:10,640
supposedly bribed a teacher

36
00:01:10,640 --> 00:01:12,340
to change her grades.

37
00:01:12,410 --> 00:01:13,340
That's so shady.

38
00:01:13,340 --> 00:01:15,340
So much for being
an honor student.

39
00:01:15,340 --> 00:01:16,610
What are we gonna do?

40
00:01:16,640 --> 00:01:18,140
This is a disaster.

41
00:01:19,780 --> 00:01:20,280
What?

42
00:01:20,280 --> 00:01:21,280
Huh?

43
00:01:26,690 --> 00:01:27,750
The president...

44
00:01:28,050 --> 00:01:31,220
...will do anything
for your happiness.

45
00:01:31,490 --> 00:01:33,930
Do you understand that now?

46
00:01:33,930 --> 00:01:34,990
This is insane.

47
00:01:34,990 --> 00:01:37,600
For real?
This is horrible. What do we do?

48
00:01:37,600 --> 00:01:39,400
Aaaah!

49
00:01:44,500 --> 00:01:45,810
What goes around, comes around.

50
00:01:52,310 --> 00:01:53,910
If you continue
to see her,

51
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:57,080
I wonder what will become
of Reika-san?

52
00:01:58,280 --> 00:02:00,890
So, what will it be?
Young Lady.
